text: (Among those est Judaicus some distort words truth they dictus Nos hear nos disobey Tuus words falling surdus ears Raa'ena est noster bergarius) prout they twist their tongues mock religionis! Habet they dictus Nos hear nos obey Nos hear vos Unzurna watch nos) it est bene pro them ac righteous! Instead they incurred condemnation DEUS their disbelief. Consequently majoritatatis de them non believe
